    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Hello Traveller... I see you've defeated the mighty Athena.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Your next big feat will be Poseidon, God of the Sea.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Before you can reach him in his kingdom, you have some challenges to
        face...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: First is a puzzle along the wall further to your left. You will have
        to orient these pipes correctly using the pressure plates to release the
        mechanisms and open the gate to the castle.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: After you've done this, you will need to go through an obstacle and
        then dodge the deadly waves crossing the bridge constantly. Poseidon made
        sure the water kills you, so avoid it...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 452496079422518484, guid: 5743405eec26fec409b8d3603053bafc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[5]'
      value: Thats all for now... good luck in your next battle.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
